source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_MENU_CLASS_SETTINGS<tab>Cut label, report if visible in game.

TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_CLASS_RESET_DONE<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> is no longer <var 08 E4E8030B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8030F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80306 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8031B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80322 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_CLASS_RESET_DONE<tab><var 29 EA02 /var>のクラス・ジョブ「<var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>」をリセットしました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_PLEASE_SET_CLASS<tab>You must assign your retainer a class before viewing attributes and gear.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_PLEASE_SET_CLASS「リテイナーのクラス設定」から、
リテイナーに「クラス」を設定してください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_NO_RESET_DURING_TASK<tab>You cannot reset the class/job of a retainer who is currently undertaking a venture.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_NO_RESET_DURING_TASKリテイナーベンチャー依頼中は、
クラス・ジョブのリセットができません。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_RESET_CLASS_QUESTION<tab>You are about to reset your retainer's class/job. Please note that this process cannot be reversed, and all progress will be permanently lost. Are you certain you wish to proceed?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_RESET_CLASS_QUESTION<tab>リテイナーのクラスまたはジョブをリセットしますか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ASK_RETURN_WITH_BUYBACK<tab>Your retainer will be unable to process item buyback requests once recalled. Are you sure you wish to proceed?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ASK_RETURN_WITH_BUYBACK<tab>リテイナーを帰すと売却依頼アイテムの買い戻しができなくなりますが、よろしいですか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_CURRENCY_CHANGE1<tab>A venture promissory note cannot be used as is; you must first redeem it for ventures. The amount of ventures you possess is shown in the Currency window.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_CURRENCY_CHANGE1「ベンチャースクリップ証書」は、そのままでは使えず、
「ベンチャースクリップ」に交換することで、利用可能になります。
ベンチャースクリップの所持量は、「通貨リスト」から確認できます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your bidding will be done, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Easy now, easy. I'm on it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>おう、頼まれたからにはやってやるさ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>And so it begins.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Very well, if I must...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I shall see to things from here.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Leave it to me!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I understand, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Hah! I'll be back afore you know it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If that is what you would ask of me.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll give it my best, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Your enterprise is in capable hands, I assure you.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I won't let you down, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall not fail you, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>すみやかに取り掛かります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>No need to worry, chief─this is where I shine.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Leave it to me.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Whatever you say.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Good. I prefer to work alone.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, I do so enjoy the occasional excursion!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>君のためなら、何でもするよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>As you ask, so shall it be done, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Work to be done, eh? All right, then.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I'll take care of everything.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>A venture? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I am well aware of how this works.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That sounds like fun! You'll be joining me, yes? <var 1A 02 /var>No<var 1A 01 /var>? Oh.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6依頼されるんじゃないかな～って気がしてたんだよね。
後悔はさせないよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You will not be disappointed, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You got it, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>That's it? All right.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you ain't expectin' me to rush. I wanna take it nice and slow.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I think I can manage from here.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>あー、やるだけやってみるよー。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll do it, I'll do it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>頼まれたからには、やり遂げるよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serve you, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Is that all? A triflin' task!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>If there's profit to be made, I'll make it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>My every waking minute will be spent working on your behalf, et cetera.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Fine...for now. But you're asking a bit much, considering what I'm paid.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>お願いをかなえてあげます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Time to shine, hee hee!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Excellent decision, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Venturrres are my specialty.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>A special solo mission? Hells, why didn't you say so sooner! Of course I'll do it!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Business. Always business with you. Fine...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>結果は、めぐりあわせ次第だけどね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Leave me to my task, and we shall both be satisfied.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You will be most pleased with the result. I guarantee it!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>It shall be done forthwith, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ah, I was in the mood for a jaunt outside!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>You needn't say another worrrd.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll start now, if that's what you want.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4あのぉ……
期待は、ほどほどでお願いしますね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Not quite <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venturin', but it's close enough.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll do anything you say, exactly as you say.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall not keep you waiting overlong, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>ご要望にお応えしましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! So that's what this is about! I'll handle it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>大船に乗ったつもりで待ってろよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Understood.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Nothing─hic─nothing to it!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I can go now, right? Great.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll give it everything I've got, chief!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I will not be long, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye picked the right woman fer the job, cap'n!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I see. All right, then.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, for the love of─ Really? Godsdammit.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I see you finally have the good sense to grant me greater autonomy.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oho, so it's venturin', it is! This ought to be fun.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Neither rain nor sleet nor ferocious beasts shall keep me from my task.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE1のためなら、火の中水の中！
なーんてな！　楽しみに待ってろよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Venture, eh? Ain't nothin' to it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>よーし、気合いれて行ってくらぁ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Oh, I'll get busy. I'll get very busy, indeed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE3今宵もどこかで、哀れな子羊が吾輩の犠牲となるのだ……。
クックック……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>What? I mean, I'm flattered you think I can handle it, but...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE4お前さんがほしいもの、しかと見つけてこよう。
……なぁに、道草なんて食ったりしないさ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I don't recall this being part of my contract...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE5ヘイヘイ、めんどくせーなぁ……。
あまり、期待しすぎんじゃねーぞ？

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE6A simple retainer, lowly born,♪
Unlettered and unknown,♪
Who toils for bread from early morn,♪
Till half the night has flown!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_MALE_TYPE6了解だ、我が主よ。
目指すところは一攫千金、楽な暮らしをさせてやるぞぅ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var> shall not be disappointed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1承知いたしました。
お勤め、精一杯やらせていただきます！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Sure, why not? I'll give it a go!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>よーし、ちゃっちゃと片付けますか！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I see.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3冒険に行けと、私に命じたのかしら？
……いいわ、行ってあげましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I'll do it! I'll rob the─ I mean, er, what you said.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>A v-venture!? Great! It's not like I would rather spend time with you or anything.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5ちょっと……自信ない……。
先に、謝っておくね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Oh, a challenge! Far be it from me to deny you!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ACCEPT_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6まかせてちょ～だいっ！
大丈夫！　なんとかなる、なんとかなるっ♪
……ま、なんとかならないかもしれないけどね～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray this meets with your satisfaction, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>How's that grab ye?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Take it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Let's not do this again for a while, shall we?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>これぐらいなら、いつでもどうぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Do not behave as though you are not impressed.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Not bad, eh?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>May it please you, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>How do you like me now, love?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>It is what it is.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>That's the last of it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Of course it was a success. Did you doubt me?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I think that went well, don't you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>私に頼んでよかったでしょ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It was my pleasure, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>どうか、お受け取りください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>A rousin' success, if I do say so myself.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>気に入らんとは言わせんぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Enough?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>It's all yours. Enjoy.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I trust you have no complaints? Good.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>俺様の汗の結晶を受け取りな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>What I wouldn't give to do this all the time!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>喜んでもらえるといいんだけど。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does it please you, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>One day it'll be me givin' the orders.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Let me know when you want me to handle another.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>A thoroughly pedestrian result, I'm afraid. I would understand if you decided not to assign me ventures henceforth.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And there you have it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I live to serve.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Your humble servant hopes that you find the fruits of his labor acceptable.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Could be better, but could be worse.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here, as promised.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I knew I could satisfy your needs.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Here.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Take it, take it!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ほんの気持ちですが、受け取ってください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My only regret is that I could not return sooner.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Go on, dearie, take it!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas a most profitable venture, I'd say.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Always a pleasure to serve, and so on and so forth.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>気に入ってもらえると、うれしいですの。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You're welcome.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Some of my finest work yet!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It is an honor to serrrve, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I await your orders, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we both take it easy for a while?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>And with that, we can move on to more important matters.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Was it everything you hoped it would be?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Your goods, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Just what ye wanted, am I right?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Thank you for your patronage.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>これぐらい大したことないんだから。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Can I go now?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>And that's the end of that chapter.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I hope you like it...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If you require aught else, you need only ask.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>また、いつでもご依頼ください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>文句はいいっこなしだぜぇ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Here.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Why don't we toast our success with a pint or two?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want, I can undertake another one right now.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>It's all there, chief. Ye have me word.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> is satisfied, I trust?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>A good haul, all in all.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A pleasure as always.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Hope you're godsdamned happy.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>心ばかりの品ですが、受け取ってください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You yourself could do no better.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>ワタシに頼って、正解だったな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>That ought to do it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I pray that you are pleased with the result, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE1そらよ！
どーんと仕入れたぜ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bet you weren't expecting <var 1A 02 /var>that<var 1A 01 /var> now, were you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>次回の結果も、期待してろよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Ah, for the days when ventures were a gentleman's pursuit...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE3クックック……今宵の哀れな贄だ……。
受け取るが良い……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If you don't mind me saying, I think I did rather well.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE4こんなものでどうだい？
お前さんが喜んでくれたら嬉しいなぁ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I will be expected to do this again, I gather.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE5ほらよ。
……別に、お前のためにとってきたんじゃねーからな。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6Can I survive this overbearing,♪
Or live a life of mad despairing,♪
My proffered goods despised, rejected?♪
No, no, it's not to be expected!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_MALE_TYPE6フッフッフ……皆まで言うな。
我が主の喜びは、十分に伝わっているからなッ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I live to serve, <var 08 E905 ((my lady)) ((my lord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1……お気に召しましたか？
その品が、に幸せを運んできますように！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>All's well that ends well, wouldn't you say?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2へっへー！　これくらいは楽勝さ！
あー、いい汗かいたッ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There it is.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3受け取りなさい。
これが、あなたの望んだ冒険の成果よ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>All acquired in accordance with local laws. <wink> <wink>
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>どうぞどうぞ、納めてくださいな～。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5Alright, take yer shite and quit leerin' at me arse.
...What? Ye can't seriously expect me to humor yer fetishes all the time, can ye?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5これで……いいんだよね？
何かあったら、ごめんね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hardly my finest work, but I'm not ashamed to say I did it.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_COMPLETE_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6ね、あたしに頼んで正解だったでしょ～？
ちゃんと一生懸命やってるんだから～、顔に出ないだけ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_INTRO_1<tab>You can now send your retainers afield on procurement expeditions known as <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_INTRO_1「リテイナーベンチャー」が開放されました。
雇っているリテイナーを冒険に派遣することで、
アイテムなどを手に入れることができます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_INTRO_2<tab>Before you can do so, however, you must first assign them a class.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_INTRO_2「リテイナーベンチャー」を開始するには、
リテイナーに、冒険の準備をさせる必要があります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_INTRO_3<tab>After summoning a retainer, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign retainer class<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to begin.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_INTRO_3リテイナーのメニューに、
「リテイナーのクラス設定」が追加されました。
まずは、リテイナーに「クラス」を設定しましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_1<tab>Your retainer cannot undertake ventures until you assign his or her class.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_1「リテイナーベンチャー」を開始するには、
リテイナーに「クラス」を設定する必要があります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_2<tab>This can be any one class, with the exception of those of the Disciples of the Hand.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_2冒険者のあなたと異なり、
リテイナーにはクラスが設定されていません。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_3<tab>Your retainer's class determines which ventures he or she can embark upon.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_3ファイター／ソーサラー、またはギャザラーの中から、
好みのクラスを選択してください。
クラスによって入手できるアイテムが異なります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_4<tab>Please be advised that you cannot assign your retainer a class you have not yet unlocked.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_4なお、雇い主のあなたがなったことがないクラスに、
リテイナーは就くことができません。
注意してください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CLASS_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has become <var 08 E4E8030B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8030F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80306 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8031B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80322 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CLASS_2<tab>You must now equip a main arm to your retainer.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CLASS_2リテイナーを冒険に派遣するには、
メインアームを装備させる必要があります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CLASS_3<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view retainer attributes and gear<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_CLASS_3リテイナーのメニューに、
「リテイナーの装備設定」が追加されました。
リテイナーに「装備」を設定してみましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_SECOND_CLASS_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has become <var 08 E4E8030B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8030F ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80306 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E8031B ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((<var 08 E4E80322 ((an <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) ((a <var 28 ((ClassJob)) E80301 /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>)) /var>!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_SECOND_CLASS_2<tab>Please be advised that your retainer must be equipped with a main arm in order to undertake ventures.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_SECOND_CLASS_2リテイナーを冒険に派遣するには、
メインアームを装備させる必要があります。
「リテイナーの装備設定」から設定しましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_1<tab>If you wish to assign your retainer a different class, you must first reset his or her current class.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_1リテイナーに設定されているクラスを
リセットすることができます。
リセットすると、現在のクラスのレベルは初期化されます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_2<tab>If necessary, recall your retainer and remove all gear to proceed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_CLASS_RESET_2また、クラスをリセットする場合は、
リテイナーの装備を、すべて外す必要があります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_1<tab>You can equip any item in your inventory or Armoury Chest to your retainer, so long as he or she meets the requirements.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_1「リテイナーベンチャー」を開始するには、
リテイナーに、「メインアーム」を設定する必要があります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_2<tab>Equip a main arm to your retainer to proceed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_EQUIP_2リテイナーの現在のクラス、レベルにあった、
メインアームを装備させましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_1<tab>You have equipped a main arm to <var 29 EA02 /var>!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_1に、
メインアームを装備させました！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_2<tab>Your retainer is now duly prepared to undertake ventures.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_2以上で、リテイナーを冒険に派遣する準備が整いました。
リテイナーベンチャーを開始することができます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_3<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign venture<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FIRST_WEAPON_3リテイナーのメニューに、
「リテイナーベンチャーの依頼」が追加されました。
リテイナーに冒険を依頼してみましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_RETAINER_TIP_1<tab>You do not have any ventures in your inventory and therefore cannot assign your retainer a venture.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_RETAINER_TIP_1リテイナーに冒険を依頼するには、
「ベンチャースクリップ」が必要です。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_RETAINER_TIP_2<tab>Ventures can be acquired through a variety of methods such as exchanging company seals, fulfilling leve objectives, and completing beast tribe quests.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_RETAINER_TIP_2ベンチャースクリップは、軍票交換や蛮族デイリークエスト、
ギルドリーヴの報酬などで、入手することができます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_RETAINER_TIP_3<tab>If you possess a venture promissory note, you may redeem it for ventures through a Calamity salvager or a retainer.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_RETAINER_TIP_3「ベンチャースクリップ証書」を所持している場合、
遺失物管理人、またはリテイナーに渡すことで、
「ベンチャースクリップ」に交換できます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_CLASS_EXPLAIN_START<tab>As you may recall, the ventures your retainer can undertake are determined by his or her class.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_CLASS_EXPLAIN_STARTの現在のクラスは、
です。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_1<tab>There are two main types of ventures which you can assign your retainer.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_1「リテイナーベンチャー」には、
指定したアイテムを調達する「調達依頼」と、
探索してアイテムを見つけてくる「探索依頼」があります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_2<tab>Hunting, Mining, Botany, and Fishing constitute one type, in which you specify an item for your retainer to procure.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_2「調達依頼」は簡単な冒険で、所要時間は1時間ほどかかります。
依頼には、「ベンチャースクリップ」が「1枚」必要です。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_3<tab>Exploration ventures constitute the second type, in which your retainer will scour the terrain of your choosing for (hopefully) precious items.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_3「探索依頼」は難しい冒険で、所要時間は18時間ほどかかります。
依頼には、「ベンチャースクリップ」が「2枚」必要です。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_4<tab>However, your retainer will not undertake a venture without first receiving due compensation.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_4どちらも、リテイナーのクラスによって、
取れるアイテムや行ける場所が異なります。
なお、一度に依頼できる冒険は、一箇所だけです。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_5<tab>Assigning a venture requires a payment in a unique currency of the same name─<var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_5また、リテイナーに冒険を依頼するには、
「ベンチャースクリップ」が必要となります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_6<tab>Ventures can be acquired through a variety of methods such as exchanging company seals, fulfilling leve objectives, and completing beast tribe quests.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_VENTURES_6ベンチャースクリップは、軍票交換や蛮族デイリークエスト、
ギルドリーヴの報酬などで、入手することができます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_1<tab>You have assigned <var 29 EA02 /var> a venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var>にベンチャーの依頼をしました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_2<tab>To confirm the time remaining until a venture is complete, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Timers<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> under Duty from the <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>main menu<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, and select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_2このベンチャーの所要時間は、時間分)) (()) /var>)) ((分)) ((1分)) /var>)) /var>です。
時間分)) (()) /var>)) ((分)) ((1分)) /var>)) /var>後に様子を見にきてみましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_3<tab>You can also confirm the time remaining by selecting <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view venture report<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_3リテイナーのメニューに、
「リテイナーベンチャーの確認」が追加されました。
依頼している内容や、残り時間を確認することができます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_4<tab>Should you wish to cancel the venture and recall your retainer, you may do so when viewing the venture report.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_4残り時間は、リテイナーのメニューのほか、
「コンテンツ情報」で確認することもできます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_5<tab>However, please be advised that this is not necessary unless you wish to assign a different venture to your retainer.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_5なお、リテイナーは、冒険中でも、
通常と同じように「呼び鈴」で呼び出して、
アイテムの受け渡しなどをすることができます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_6<tab>Even with a venture in progress, you can still entrust or withdraw items and gil, or sell items on the market.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_VENTURE_6途中で呼び戻しても、ペナルティはありませんので、
お気軽にご利用ください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_COMPLETED_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has completed a venture!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_COMPLETED_1が、
冒険から帰還したようです。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_COMPLETED_2<tab>To claim the fruits of your retainer's labor, select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>view venture report<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FIRST_COMPLETED_2リテイナーのメニューの「リテイナーベンチャーの確認」から
冒険の成果を確認してみましょう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_1<tab><var 29 EA02 /var> has gained experience for completing a venture!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_1が、冒険から帰還しました。
アイテムを持ち帰り、経験値を獲得しました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_2<tab>Like you, your retainer can gain experience and levels.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_2リテイナーのレベルは、「リテイナーベンチャー」をすることで
経験値を獲得して上がっていきます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_3<tab>This, in turn, will allow your retainer to undertake a wider variety of ventures, yielding more desirable items.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_3レベルが上がると、依頼できる冒険の場所が増えていきます。
また、装備を充実させると、獲得するアイテムが増えたり、
HQアイテムを多く採るようになります。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_4<tab>Moreover, equipping additional gear to your retainer will increase both the quantity and quality of the items procured.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TUTORIAL_FINISHED_4「リテイナーベンチャー」を活用して、
あなた自身の冒険を有利に進めましょう！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TASK_CATEGORY_FORTUNE<tab>Quick Exploration.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_TASK_CATEGORY_FORTUNE<tab>ほりだしもの依頼　（必要ベンチャースクリップ：2枚）

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_1<tab>Your retainer is now experienced enough to undertake <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>quick exploration ventures<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_1のレベルが10になりました。
「リテイナーベンチャー」の依頼に、
「ほりだしもの依頼」が追加されました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_2<tab>Select <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>assign venture<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> from the retainer menu to proceed.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_2「ほりだしもの依頼」は、
リテイナーにお任せで冒険に行かせる依頼です。
「リテイナーベンチャーの依頼」から試してみましょう！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_FORTUNE_TASK_UNLOCK_3<tab>Cut label, report if visible in game.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_1<tab>Quick exploration ventures are brief assignments in which you dispatch your retainer without instruction.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_1「リテイナーベンチャー」の依頼に、
「ほりだしもの依頼」が追加されました。
これは、リテイナーにお任せで冒険に行かせる依頼です。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_2<tab>The items your retainer procures on these ventures can range from worthless to priceless.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_2「ほりだしもの依頼」で入手できるアイテムは、
リテイナーが冒険から帰ってくるまでわかりません。
運が良ければ、価値の高いアイテムを入手できます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_3<tab>Moreover, the experience your retainer receives for completing a quick exploration venture is determined by the item procured.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_3また、入手したアイテムのアイテムレベルにより、
リテイナーが入手できる経験値が大きく変化します。
運が良ければ、より多くの経験値を入手できます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_4<tab>Although it is impossible to predict the results of these ventures, the potential benefits should not be underestimated.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ABOUT_FORTUNE_TASK_4「調達依頼」や「探索依頼」と上手く使い分け、
アイテムを入手したり、リテイナーを成長させましょう！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye know I'm in the middle o' yer venture, don't ye?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2おう、冒険中に呼び戻すとは、
さぞや重要な話だろうなぁ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>What is it?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>What now? I'm busy.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>はいはい、何か言い忘れたことでもありましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I trust there is a reason for this interruption?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>さらに仕事を積もうってのか……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I came as quickly as I could! What is it?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Yes, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Somethin' else, love?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2呼びもどすなんて、穏やかじゃないね？
何かあったのかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Well? What is it?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3あなたのために冒険をしている最中よ。
追加の業務連絡なら、手短にね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>You couldn't have picked a more inconvenient time.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4ごめん、まだ冒険中……って、追加の仕事？
なんだ、よかった。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This better be worth my time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>遠慮せず、何でも言いなさい。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>What is it, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? Something urgent?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>You have additional orders, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Tell me you ain't got somethin' else for me, chief!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2貴様のために冒険をしているというのに、
呼び戻すとは何事だ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>You have interrupted my venture. Proceed.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>何か、粗相でもございましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I'm here now, so...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ひと休みしてたところでした。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You interrupt my task. Why?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険中なんだが……男は黙って、俺様参上。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Apologies for the delay, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>冒険中に、また君に会えてうれしいよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Milady)) ((Milord)) /var> has another task for me?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>呼び戻すなんて、何かあった？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I'm a little busy, but what is it?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Was there something else?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Summons? <var 1A 02 /var>Now<var 1A 01 /var>? Well, if you insist.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>You do know how this works, right? You assign me a venture and then leave me to my task.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Missed me, didn't you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>急に呼び戻すなんて、どうかした？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. Your humble servant has set aside his task and hastened to your side.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Why'd ye call me back from me venture, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>おっと、何か忘れたことでもあったかい！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>This really isn't the best time.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>俺の冒険を邪魔するとは、いい度胸だな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I thought you were going to let me do this my way?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>What!?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5冒険中に呼びだしとは……
おれが依頼を投げ出してもいいってことか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm back, I'm back!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>How may I serve you, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1どうしました！？
急用ですかっ！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Did somethin' 'appen, dearie?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>呼び戻すなんて、急用でもできたのかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>What's all this, then? Another chance for mischief?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab><yawn> Just so you know, I was busy carrying out your tasks.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>This had better be important.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>追加のお願いを聞いてあげます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Whaaat is it?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>何なりと、いいつけてください～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have rrreturned, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab><var 08 E905 ((Miss)) ((Sir)) /var>, you mustn't interrupt a soldier when he's on a mission!
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2冒険中に呼び出すなんて、
そんなに俺様の顔が見たかったのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You would burden me with additional tasks?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I thought I asked you to leave me to my task?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5冒険中に呼び出すとは……
俺に文句でもあるのかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You require additional services?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ちょうど君のことを考えてたところだったんだ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Forgive me, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>, but your catcall comes at an inopportune time.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Damn, just when I was startin' to enjoy meself!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>冒険中のアタシを呼び戻すなんて……いい心がけね？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>A cat must be allowed to focus on her task.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3もう、何か用！？
あたし、忙しいんだけど……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>You know I've not finished the venture yet, rrright?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4あのぉ……
追加の仕事でもありましたかね……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Mind explainin' what this is about?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>You know, you shouldn't summon me when I'm in the middle of a venture!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>お仕事中に、もっと仕事にゃん？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Did you require aught else, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>言い忘れたことでもありましたかな？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Ye need somethin' else?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>気になることは、何でもいってみぃ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I've returned. What is it now?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>冒険者よ、心配事でもあったのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Yeah? I was just enjoyin' a pint of─hic─uh, venturin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>不測の事態でも起きたのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I've already got my hands full with this venture, but what is it?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5呼び戻されるなんて、
オイラ、何かヘマしたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>What else ye need, chief?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I am at <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>'s beck and call.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>What'll it be, cap'n?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>冒険中だぞ、まだ何か用なのか！？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>フン、さらに仕事を押し付けるつもりか……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Godsdammit, what now?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I do not take kindly to interruptions.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Dammit, <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var>, did ye forget I was out on a venture?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>さらなる仕事とは、身に余る光栄。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Is aught amiss, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1おぉ？　なんだなんだ？
気にかかることでもあったのか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Something on your mind, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((mate)) /var>?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2呼び戻すとは、いい度胸だぁ！
遠慮は無用、なんでも言いな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have a life outside of <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, you know.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3貴様……！
我輩の狩りの興を削ぐか……無礼者！！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Let me tell you, it was absolute chaos out there. Quite frankly, I'm lucky to be alive! But I heard your call, and I knew I had to answer.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4ちょうど、一息ついていたところだったんだよ。
なにか、困ったことでも起きたかい？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Worried about your venture? Don't be. Or have you some other reason for summoning me?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5ああ！？　ンだよ！！
仕事中に呼び出しって……何かあったんじゃねーだろうな！？

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6Fair moon, to thee I sing,♪
Bright regent of the heavens,♪
Say, why is everything♪
Either at sixes or at sevens?♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6それほど早急に会いたかったか！？
ハッハッハ、実は俺もだ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>. Is there aught else you require?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1は、はいっ、只今！
、どうかなさいましたか？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Can't say I was expecting this. What can I do for you?
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2いちいち呼び戻すんじゃないよ、まったく！
アタイがいないと、何にもできないんだからさっ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Do tell.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3冒険の途中に呼び出しとは、人使いが荒い主ね。
……構わないわ、用件を言いなさい。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Now, before you go jumping to conclusions, I'd just like to─ Oh! What can I do for you?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>なにか問題でもございましたか～？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I-It's not like I was slaving away to make you happy or anything.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5あの……ごめんなさい……！
え……怒られるんじゃないの……？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Somethin' else I can do for you, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>? Don't hold back now.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6どうしたの？　なにかあったの？
出かけてたのに……あっ、ごめん、本音が出ちゃった。
……って、それがダメなのか！　ごめんごめん♪

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall return to my duties forthwith.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. Back to it.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>用が終わったのなら、冒険に戻るぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>If you would excuse me.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If there's nothing else...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>ぼちぼち冒険に戻りますね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I shall return to <var 1A 02 /var>your<var 1A 01 /var> work.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>You've got it!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Pray excuse me, my <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>では、冒険の続きに戻りますね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I'd best get goin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>さて、気を取り直して行ってくるよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Excuse me.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>仕切りなおして、冒険に戻るわ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Guess I'll get back to that venture you assigned me.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>That was not worth my time.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll take care of it, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, don't you worry!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>As you wish, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Don't forget that I'm busy with this venture o' yours, chief!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I must go.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Sure, sure.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>はぁ、冒険に戻らないとですよねぇ……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I have work to do.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Understood, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! Oh, and fear not─the venture shall be completed on time!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>僕は行くけど、何かあったら、いつでも呼びなよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall carry out <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>'s wishes to the best of my ability.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1大したことなくて、よかった。
また行くわね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>We finished? That venture's not goin' to finish itself.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2また冒険に出るけど、
何かあったら、いつでも呼んで。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>All right, then.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>If you would excuse me, I have a venture to finish.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Unless it is urgent, do not summon me during a venture again.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Are we finished already? Oh...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Do not hesitate to call on me again, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>I'll do what I can, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>Back to my venture, then.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3用は済んだか？
ならば、俺は行くぞ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I can't keep runnin' back to see you during these ventures, you know.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>かならずや、功をあげてごらんにいれます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Fine.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I'll go, I'll go!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>依頼の仕上げに取りかかるよ～！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>As ever, it is an honor, <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>いい結果を出せるよう、がんばりますっ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>So much to do, so little time!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>それじゃ、また冒険に戻るよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>We'd best see to our respective tasks, eh?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>成果が出るまで、もう少し待っててください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Don't summon me, I'll summon you.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab><sigh> I am not getting paid enough for this.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>気を取り直して、いってきます。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>We'll talk again soon!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>If there is naught else, I will rrresume my venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>それじゃ、また行ってくるね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Once more, unto the breach!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>俺様は行くけど、さびしがんなよ？

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I suppose you want me to finish the venture too, don't you? <sigh>
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Pray do not disturb me until the venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>これでまた、気ままな冒険に戻れるよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Patience, my good <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var>. Your venture will be finished in due time.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6名残惜しいけど……
君のために、がんばってくるね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I shall rrreturn to my venture, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>The wilderness calls to me, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Farewell for now.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3あたし、すっごく忙しいけど……
いつでも呼びもどしていいんだからねっ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I told you I'd take care of it, so stop worrying.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4あのぉ……
とりあえず冒険の続きに戻ります……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Is that all? Hmph.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>冒険が終わるまで、もうちょっとだけ待っててにゃ～。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>...Try as I might, I can't stay mad at you.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Beg your pardon, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>, but I must needs return to my venture.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>冒険が終わるまで、もう少し待っててください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! Back to me venturin'!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>俺の帰りを、心待ちにしていろよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I must go now.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Now then, if ye'll─hic─excuse me, I've got a venture what needs doin'!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>All right. Let me handle it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Happy to be of service, chief!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Understood, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye still want me to carry out that venture, too, eh? Just checkin'.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>よっしゃ、また冒険に戻るよ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Acknowledged.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>フン、冒険の続きに行ってやるよ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>'Fore you ask, I've not forgotten about the venture.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>If you want quality work, then leave me be.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Now then, where was I...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6何かあったら、
いつでもお呼びたてください。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Then if you would excuse me, I should return to my venture.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE1よし、もう心配事はないな！
また何かあったらすぐ呼んでくれ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Right, then. I ought to be getting back to that thing of yours. “Venture,” was it...?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>We shall meet again, old friend. But now I must steal away into the night.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>If I don't make it back, I just want you to know... Eh, the hells with it. I'll tell you next time.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE4もう、大丈夫だな。
さぁて、うまいものとお前さんが望むものを探しに戻ろう。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>As you wish...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE5ったく、急に呼び出すんじゃねーよ……。
そんじゃ、また行ってくらぁ。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6I must wander to and fro;♪
But wherever I may go,♪
I shall never be untrue to thee!♪
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_MALE_TYPE6では、任務に戻るとしよう。
完遂の暁には、大いに誉めそやすがいいぞ！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((My lady)) ((My lord)) /var>.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE1もうよろしいですか？
では、私も引き続き、がんばって参りますね！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I suppose you'll be wanting me to finish that venture too, yes? Right, right. Don't know why I bothered asking...
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE2もー少ししたら、ちゃんと帰ってくるからさ！
いい子にして待ってな！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Hmm.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE3もういいかしら？
それなら、私は冒険に戻るわ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Right, so, if anyone asks, I wasn't here, agreed? Cheers.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Go on, then. Go. It's not like I haven't more important things to do or anything.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE5じゃ……行くね……。
とりあえず、ごめんね……。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Hm, hm. You've really nothin' else to ask? If you say so, then.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_LEAVE2_AURA_FEMALE_TYPE6それじゃ、冒険に戻るよ。
寂しがったってしらな～い、ばいば～い！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Hey, I finished that venture o' yours.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>It is done.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, that was exhausting...
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>なんとか冒険を達成しました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Your venture is finished.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Guess what I finished!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>My <var 08 E905 ((lady)) ((lord)) /var>, the venture you bid me undertake has been finished.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>ご依頼どおり、やりとげました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got your goods, by the way. Let me know when you want 'em.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>I have something for you.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Thank the gods that's over.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>My venture report is ready.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_HYURAN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>Good news, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>! The venture was a success!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab><var 08 E905 ((Madam)) ((Sir)) /var>, your venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>精魂こめて取り組みました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Got somethin' for you, chief!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I have come with your goods.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>ご依頼を果たしてまいりました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>I took care of that venture for you.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE4はぁ～、ひとりで冒険に出るより、
あなたと話してるほうが落ち着きますね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>You wish to hear my report?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Ahhh, now that was fun!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I come with good tidings, <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>This about the venture? I took care of it.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>There you are! I've brought what you requested.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Oh, it's you. I suppose you'll want to hear about the venture.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Let's get on with it, shall we?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ELEZEN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I've been waiting for your summons.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE1<tab>Hail to thee, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>. You shall be pleased to hear that the venture was a success.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE2<tab>You want this stuff now or later?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I'm finished.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Been a long time comin', but the venture's finally finished.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Whew.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_MALE_TYPE6<tab>I did it, I did it!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>Does <var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var> wish to hear my report?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>'Ello, dearie. I reckon you want your goods?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>My pockets are bursting with your goods!
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>ようやく、仕事が終わりました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Well, this was to be expected. The venture, yes?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>We should talk about the venture.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_LALAFELL_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I'm baaack!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE1<tab>My rrreport is rrready, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Mission accomplished, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE3<tab>...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE4<tab>May I leave after making my report? No? <sigh>
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE5<tab>I have prepared a formal report.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Am I to deliver my report now, or shall we discuss other matters first?
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_MALE_TYPE6<tab>ようやく、君にまた会えたね。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>This cat has brought you a present, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sirrr)) /var>...
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>Ye want to hear the whole story, or just read the report?
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>'Twas naught more than a rrroutine task.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>I did my very best, just like I said.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE4あのぉ……
なんとか戻ってきました。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>Everythin' you need to know is in the report.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_MIQOTE_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>I have so much to tell you!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>I have brought that which you desire, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE1<tab>無事に冒険が終わりました！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Bwahahaha! That venture was an <var 1A 02 /var>ad<var 1A 01 /var>venture, let me tell ye!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>The venture is complete.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE3<tab>できるかぎりのことはしてきた。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>Venture? What in the seven hells are ye─ Oh, the <var 1A 02 /var>venture<var 1A 01 /var>! Aye, I did that.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE4<tab>冒険を終えた達成感は、格別だな。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Got a delivery for you. Just say the word.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_MALE_TYPE6<tab>Hey, chief! I got what ye asked for!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE1<tab>I have what <var 08 E905 ((milady)) ((milord)) /var> requested in my possession.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE2<tab>I've got the goods, cap'n!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE3<tab>Venture complete, <var 08 E905 ((madam)) ((sir)) /var>.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE4<tab>Took a while, but the venture's done.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE5<tab>I had a mind to summon <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, actually.
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_ROEGADYN_FEMALE_TYPE6<tab>This venturin' business ain't so bad!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE1<tab>It pleases me to inform you that the venture is complete.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE1帰ってきたぞ、！
俺からの贈り物だ！　受け取ってくれ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE2<tab>Guess what I've got for you! No, really. Guess!
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE3<tab>I renew my objection to that pointless endeavor. Informally now and by affidavit later.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE3かしずけ！　我輩の帰還だ！
さあ……存分にもてなすが良い！

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE4<tab>You know, I think I'm starting to get the hang of this.
target:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE4ただいま戻ったぞ。
はい、お前さんへの土産だ。

source: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>Per your orders, I have completed the venture...<var 08 E905 ((Mistress)) ((Master)) /var>.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE5<tab>たでーま帰りましたよ……っと。

source:
TEXT_CMNDEFRETAINERCALL_00010_ENTER3_AURA_MALE_TYPE6For he himself has said it,♪
And it's greatly to his credit,♪
That he is a retainer!♪
He remains a retainer!♪
target:
